<div id="review_2953378271" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2953378271" />
    <a title="Sharone Powell" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/8987415-sharone-powell"><img alt="Sharone Powell" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1335192704p2/8987415.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2953378271?book_show_action=true">Sep 04, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sharone Powell" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sharone Powell" href="/user/show/8987415-sharone-powell">Sharone Powell</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2953378271" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5032191461538623914">Giovanni Tempesta dreams of becoming an opera singer. He struggles to make his dream a reality in front of great odds. There is much to like in this story. The plot is reminiscent of many opera plots--very melodramatic, in order to stir the emotions. Of course, we need it in opera, since music and emotions go hand in hand. If you&apos;re an opera fan and would like to learn more about it in a fun way, this book is for you.</span>
  <span id="freeText5032191461538623914" style="display:none">Giovanni Tempesta dreams of becoming an opera singer. He struggles to make his dream a reality in front of great odds. There is much to like in this story. The plot is reminiscent of many opera plots--very melodramatic, in order to stir the emotions. Of course, we need it in opera, since music and emotions go hand in hand. If you're an opera fan and would like to learn more about it in a fun way, this book is for you.</span>
