  <span id="freeText6451193807483907456" style="display:none">I loved this book. I cared about the characters, shared their passion for love and opera and consider Mr. LoCoco's book to be one of my favorites. This book was inspiring to me. I am a young college student pursuing classical voice that dreams of being a professional singer. Each page taught me more about my craft. I plan on recommending the book to my opera and musical theatre college friends. The ending was so beautiful! It reminded me of the relationship I have with my first voice teacher. He has done so much for me and although I am in college studying under a different teacher, I still take lessons from him semi regularly. Read this book!</span>
