        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer783255803" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8990914823095111026">This was such a wonderful book. Its a great story, full of passion and admirable characters. I learned so much about different operas that I didn&apos;t know before. Its a great insight into what goes on behind the scenes for those involved in opera. I&apos;m really looking forward to reading another book by this author.</span>
  <span id="freeText8990914823095111026" style="display:none">This was such a wonderful book. Its a great story, full of passion and admirable characters. I learned so much about different operas that I didn't know before. Its a great insight into what goes on behind the scenes for those involved in opera. I'm really looking forward to reading another book by this author.</span>
