        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer977911554" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14784714354195054033">Written very simplistically and the characters were a bit flat. It felt like the book was a vehicle for talking about opera, not really much of a story by itself. However, I did enjoy the ending and it did have a few unpredictable bits throughout. It would be fantastic if it would be sold with the music. It would definitely enhance the enjoyment of a very simple story.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


